      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The text-shadow property adds shadow to text."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "In its simplest use, you only specify the horizontal shadow (2px) and the vertical shadow (2px):"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Text shadow effect!"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "h1\n{\n  text-shadow: 2px 2px;\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Next, add a color (red) to the shadow:"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Text shadow effect!"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "h1\n{\n  text-shadow: 2px 2px red;\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Then, add a blur effect (5px) to the shadow:"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Text shadow effect!"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "unknown",
          "code": "h1\n{\n  text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px red;\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
